HEADWORD: Superlunary
<hw>Su`per*lu"na*ry</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Being above the moon; not
belonging to this world; -- opposed to <xex>sublunary</xex>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The head that turns at <qex>superlunar</qex> things.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Superman</ent>⟦br⟧
